    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>grated garlic</strong> (not a fan of raw garlic? Just add a little!) with the juice<strong> </strong>of the <strong>lemon[s] </strong>(not sure about citrus? Try using less!), 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>in a bowl<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>lemon dressing</strong></p>",
