    {
      "instruction": "<p>Strip your<strong> mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> into quarters</p><p>Crumble your<strong> Greek cheese</strong> into rough bite-sized pieces</p>",
