    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the<strong> chopped mint</strong>, <strong>cherry tomato quarters</strong>,<strong> salad</strong> and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>crumbled Greek cheese </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) to the <strong>cooked quinoa</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> lemon dressing </strong>and mix it all together – this is your<strong> quinoa salad</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>toasted pistachios</strong> roughly</p>",
