      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>roasted aubergine & courgette</strong> over the <strong>quinoa salad</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining crumbled Greek cheese</strong> and the <strong>chopped toasted pistachios</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
